Atlamtic Map, Summer 1940

Eric Rauchway

2022-06-18

Map data draws principally from Natural Earth datasets, at various resolutions. Ive drawn for reference on other sources, including Andr Ouredniks historical basemaps repository and Michael de Groots Building the New Order as well as the Rand-McNally map of Africa in 1939, from the David Rumsey Map Collection; for names of bases, Air Corps News Letter For colors I drew mainly from CARTOcolors. When all else has failed Ive looked up latitudes and longitudes in Wikipedia.
